This plugin provides MangoHud configuration management. It is an
independent implementation inspired by the MangoPeel Decky-Loader plugin:

  https://github.com/Gawah/MangoPeel
  Copyright (c) 2023 Gawah (BSD-3-Clause)

No source code from MangoPeel was copied or transliterated. This plugin
reads and writes `~/.config/MangoHud/MangoHud.conf` directly. The upstream
is credited here for inspiration and feature-parity reference only.

This plugin was previously named `mangopeel` in this repository; it was
renamed to `mangohud-tweaks` to avoid name collision with the upstream
project.
